short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds details about Ractive Components to chrome dev tools.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension provides detailed data about Ractive components in Ractive 0.7 and now 0.9

Currently provided details include:
Component name,
Data properties,
Computed properties
